  "instructions": [
    "Cook pasta according to package instructions until al dente.",
    "Meanwhile, in a medium saucepan, combine heavy cream, garlic powder, and 1 tablespoon of basil. Bring to a simmer over medium heat.",
    "Reduce heat to low, stir in butter, salt, pepper, and flour. Cook for about 2 minutes, stirring constantly, until mixture thickens slightly.",
    "Add remaining chopped basil, cheese, breadcrumbs, and panko breadcrumbs. Mix well to combine.",
    "Remove from heat and add cooked pasta, tossing gently to coat with sauce and breadcrumb mixture.",
    "Serve warm."
  ],
